  "original_title": "\u0b87\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf - \u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8 \u0b89\u0bb1\u0bb5\u0bc1 \u0b9a\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b89\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3\u0ba4\u0bc1: \u0b95\u0bcb\u0baa\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0bb2\u0bc7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Indo-Sri Lankan relations are at their best: Gopal Bagle",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "India's High Commissioner to Sri Lanka, Gopal Bagle, has said that trade and investment relations between Sri Lanka and India are in good shape.",
        "Gopal Bagle said that he is concerned about the development of port, renewable energy, hydrocarbon infrastructure and there is a need to make further investments in agriculture, dairy, information technology and higher education.",
        "He also mentioned that large companies have been representing India in Sri Lanka for decades and large Indian companies are carrying out business operations in Galle. (a)"
      ],
